Firstly, this torrent is episode 15, great job with the mis-information!

Secondly:
"Production Number & Airing Sequence are sometimes different. The Ark was
filmed after Tao of Rodney because they couldn't build the Ark in time.
Production Number is the order of which the episodes were filmed in.

Airing Sequence is the actual order that it's aired. Sci-Fi does not need to
air it for us to know the airing sequence.

Movie Central bought the airing rights for SGA. Therefore, they are airing the
episodes in order."
